          </td>        </tr>        <tr class="ipl-zebra-list__item">            <td class="ipl-zebra-list__label">Goofs</td>            <td>                Great White Sharks cannot move backwards once their gills are under water, as seen towards the end of the film.                    <a href="/title/tt0073195/goofs">See more &raquo;</a>            </td>        </tr>        <tr class="ipl-zebra-list__item">            <td class="ipl-zebra-list__label">Movie Connections</td>            <td>                Edited into<a href="/title/tt0093300/">Jaws: The Revenge</a>&nbsp;(1987).                                    <a href="/title/tt0073195/movieconnections">See more &raquo;</a>            </td>        </tr>        <tr class="ipl-zebra-list__item">            <td class="ipl-zebra-list__label">Soundtracks</td>            <td>                Show Me The Way To Go Home                    <a href="/title/tt0073195/soundtrack">See more &raquo;</a>            </td>        </tr>        <tr class="ipl-zebra-list__item">            <td class="ipl-zebra-list__label">Crazy Credits</td>            <td>                The producers gratefully acknowledge the cooperation of The Nation Geographical Society and Mr. L.J.V. Compagno of the Department of Biological Sciences, Stanford University.                    <a href="/title/tt0073195/crazycredits">See more &raquo;</a>            </td>        </tr>        <tr class="ipl-zebra-list__item">            <td class="ipl-zebra-list__label">Quotes</td>            <td><strong><a href="/name/nm0001702">Brody</a></strong>:                                         You're gonna need a bigger boat.<br>                    <a href="/title/tt0073195/quotes">See more &raquo;</a>            </td>        </tr>            </table>        </section>    </section>  <script>    if ('csm' in window) {      csm.measure('csm_TitleContributeWidget_started');    }  </script>    <div class="article contribute">        <div class="rightcornerlink"><a href="https: